Title: Increase Speed of Youtube Audio
Product: Chrome, Youtube
Description: Changes the speed of the audio on a Youtube video. 
Tags: Speed, Youtube, Audio
Steps:
1. F12 for Inspect
2. Go to Console
3. enter: 
$('video').playbackRate=x
4. hit enter

