Title: Reveal Password Field Hidden by Asterisk
Product: Chrome
Description: Bookmarklet that, when clicked, reveals a password field hidden by asterisks
Tags: bookmarklet, chrome, password
Steps:
1. Create bookmark in Chrome
2. Paste the following:
javascript:Array.prototype.slice.call(document.querySelectorAll("input[type='password']"))    .map(function(el){el.setAttribute('type','text')})

